        {
            "id": 6068750,
            "title": "外資小買3億元 買盤轉向傳產股 敲進台塑四寶4.4萬張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台股今 (17) 日在台積電尾盤回穩下，上漲 70.38 點收 23113.28 點，外資小買超 3.08 億元，大舉敲進傳產股，買超台塑四寶共 4.4 萬張，也敲進航空雙雄、面板雙虎等，反手大砍 0050 5.23 萬張。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6068750/l/e48e8b15e6896c0720e0eae0ab94e37a.jpg\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">外資小買3億元 買盤轉向傳產股 敲進台塑四寶4.4萬張。(鉅亨網資料照)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>外資今日買超華航 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2610:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2610\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2610-TW</a>)2.06 萬張最多、長榮航 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2618:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2618\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2618-TW</a>)6654 張，台塑四寶則分別買進台塑 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1301:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1301\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1301-TW</a>)1.34 萬張、南亞 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1303:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1303\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1303-TW</a>)1.27 萬張、台化 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1326:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1326\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1326-TW</a>)1.24 萬張、以及台塑化 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6505:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6505\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6505-TW</a>)5486 張，其他傳產股還有亞泥 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1102:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1102\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1102-TW</a>)1.25 萬張、中鋼 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2002:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2002\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2002-TW</a>)7919 張、遠東新 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1402:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1402\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1402-TW</a>)7685 張等。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>電子股方面，外資買超神達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3706:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3706\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3706-TW</a>)1.36 萬張、面板雙虎群創 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3481:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3481\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3481-TW</a>)1.47 萬張、友達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2409:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2409\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2409-TW</a>)8761 張，聯電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2303:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2303\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2303-TW</a>)9529 張、宏碁 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2353:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2353\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2353-TW</a>)8761 張等、泰金寶 - DR(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:9105:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/9105\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">9105-TW</a>)6893 張等。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>外資賣超多為元大台灣 50(0050)5.23 萬張，其次依序為元大台灣 50 反 1 1.73 萬張、永豐金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2890:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2890\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2890-TW</a>)1.56 萬張、華南金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2880:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2880\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2880-TW</a>)7998 張、中信金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2891:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2891\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2891-TW</a>)7214 張、定穎投控 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3715:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3715\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3715-TW</a>)6572 張，華邦電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2344:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2344\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2344-TW</a>) 及大同 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2371:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2371\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2371-TW</a>) 各 6100 多張；京元電子 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2449:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2449\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2449-TW</a>)、欣興 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3037:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3037\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3037-TW</a>)、兆豐金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2886:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2886\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2886-TW</a>) 各逾 6000 張。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
